  "westernTraditionalUsage": {
    "en": "Mineral oil or liquid petrolatum is a colourless by-product from the distillation of petroleum with excellent emollient effects. It has a wide range of uses, being the main ingredient in baby oil, petroleum jelly and many lotions and cosmetics, especially lipstick. It is also an effective make-up remover.\n",
    "zh-Hant": "精華油是嬰兒油、凡士林、其他潤膚霜和化妝品的主要成份， 特別是用作唇膏。精華油更能有效卸妝。\n",
    "zh-Hans": "精华油是婴儿油、凡士林、其他润肤霜和化妆品的主要成份， 特别是用作唇膏。精华油更能有效卸妆。\n"
  },
